title: Czech vote to decide fate of divisive president
text:
Czech vote to decide fate of divisive president Thursday, January 11, 2018 - 01:42 
An outspoken, eurosceptic and strongly anti-immigrant President - he's divided the Czech Republic, but as the country heads to vote on Friday he's expected to be chosen again.
